---
title: Spice-Rubbed Chicken with Sweet Potato, Bell Pepper, and Feta Jumble
description: Did you know that sweet potatoes aren’t actually potatoes? They’re a part of the morning glory family of flowering plants. But that doesn’t mean we love ’em any less, especially when they’re tossed with tangy feta and tender, slightly spicy chicken.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spice-rubbed-chicken-7125da75.jpg
